    "bio": "Helping you unlock your potential through masterful communication 🚀\nFree 2 Hour Training 👇",
    "descripcion": "I was SO CLOSE! 😬\n\nComment 'CHAT' if you want my free 2 hour training to stop rambling and speak more clearly.\n\nThese are the tips I shared: \n \n1. The voice you have right now isn't your natural voice it's your habitual voice.\n\n2. People form beliefs about you not just based on how you look, but also how you sound. You can buy the way you look, but you can't buy the way you sound. That's earnt.\n\n3. Stop talking at the same speed. Slow down when saying something important, otherwise speed up.\n\n4. Don't rush to answer a question. Pause first - it makes you sound more thoughtful.\n\necord a video of yourself speaking for 5 minutes and review it- self awareness is the first step to improving the way you speak\n\n6. End every sentences on a low pitch, it makes you sound more certain.\n\n7. Your posture introduces you before your words do.\n\n8. You become what you practice.\n\n9. Match the expression on your face with the emotion behind your words.\n\n10. Stop trying to be interesting. Learn how to be more interested.\n\n11. Don't report your stories, relive them.\n\n12. Stop replying to people with Yes But - start saying YES AND\n\n13. What you don't change about your communication skills, you are choosing...\n\n14. Your voice is an instrument - you don't use an instrument, you PLAY an instrument - so learn how to play it.\n\n15. Learn how to be vulnerable without bringing the mood down.\n\nWhich one's your favorite tip?!",
